    <item>
      <title>特朗普准备宣布格里尔出任美国贸易代表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-27/trump-prepares-to-announce-greer-as-us-trade-rep-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社获悉，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的过渡团队正准备宣布杰米森·格里尔出任美国贸易代表。特朗普在社交媒体上威胁对墨西哥、加拿大和中国征收关税的帖子引起了世界领导人和投资者的轰动。恩达·柯伦报道了《彭博社：亚洲贸易》。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-27/trump-prepares-to-announce-greer-as-us-trade-rep-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 01:45:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Seven & i 股价上涨 2.2%，因有报道称 KKR 有意收购超市业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/seven-i-rises-2-2-on-report-of-kkr-interest-in-supermarkets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此前有报道称 KKR &amp; Co. 正考虑投资 York Holdings，Seven &amp; i Holdings Co. 的股价上涨 2.2%。York Holdings 是一家涵盖超市、餐厅和其他资产的伞形公司，可能会从 Seven &amp; i 中分拆出来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/seven-i-rises-2-2-on-report-of-kkr-interest-in-supermarkets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 01:17:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
